  • Constructor Details

    • ArmorStandPart

      public ArmorStandPart​(MMOMob me, Boolean s, String pid, org.bukkit.util.Vector position, org.bukkit.util.EulerAngle rot, ArmorStandPart p, Integer customI)
      Create a new ArmorStandPart
      Parameters:
      me - MMOMob the armor stand is apart of
      s - If the ArmorStand needs to be small or not
      pid - The name of the part this class is representing
      position - The location the ArmorStandPart will be spawning at
      rot - Rotation the ArmorStandPart needs to be
      p - The parent of this ArmorStandPart if there is any
      customI - The CustomModelData this ArmorStandPart will send to MMOMobArmorStand to set the saddles model
